;
PROBLEM: Mu(calc) and Mu(CIF) Ratio Differs from 1.0 by .      84.00 %     
RESPONSE: CifCheck has become confused by the fractional occupancies 
of the methylammonium, and has decided that Z=1 for a cubic system is
preferable to the rational alternative of Z=8.
;
